{"tid":560507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【買完又賣】萬達傳出售馬德里體育會股份","createTime":"2018-02-14T07:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T07:09:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf6f9838092e9eb226bc2efd04d08cf0567e671","tid":560507,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180214/s00010/bf2ab629b522f59cea176b5705ea4a3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180214%2Fs00010%2Fbf2ab629b522f59cea176b5705ea4a3b.jpg&h=89e1e910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據西班牙媒體El Confidencial報道，萬達已出售馬德里競技俱樂部18%股份，交易細節尚未獲官方確認，但估計交易作價近5000萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n2015年1月，萬達宣布收購西甲馬德里競技足球俱樂部20%股份，出資4500萬歐元，是中國企業首次投資歐洲頂級足球俱樂部。去年11月，馬德里競技俱樂部引入以色列富豪Idan Ofer入股15%，令萬達持股被稀釋到18%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1518591671328&amp;issue=20180214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1518591671328%26issue%3D20180214&d=Z%2FLYlDC%2BbCiY9gyXoKvgKUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=722fb90b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1518591671328%26issue%3D20180214&h=1d511819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1518591671328&amp;issue=20180214</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 明報記者無睇波定係中國人？唔識馬體會？"}]}